data.description: Situated on over 1/2 acre, entertaining guests is a breeze with the sliding glass door that leads out to an oversized deck, perfect for hosting summer gatherings or simply unwinding by your above ground pool after a long day. The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been thoughtfully updated with stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, butcher block counters, and an island complete with a wine refrigerator, making meal prep a joyous occasion. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms and an oversized bonus room that can serve as a bedroom and office. You will love the charm of the laundry room/mudroom with butcher block accents. Start your memories that you can cherish for years to come. Welcome Home! Sketch is pending to verify square footage. AGENTS-NOT member of NCR MLS? Call Showing Time to schedule and let them know you are NOT a member and need access.
